    },
    {
      "id": "29d9cfd4-ee19-499d-81ae-2eeb82f0c56e",
      "content": "X. Mt 16,24... ; Mc 13,14-26 ; Lc 21,20-24 ; Mt 10,24.38 ; Ga 15,1...",
